QuestData.Title: A Rough Start
QuestData.Description: Lets put dose skills ta use. I'll start ya off easy, mon.$B$BThere be cats killing our boars. Dat food ain't for sharin'. Dose boars are gonna need ta be alive if ya be wanting food tonight.$B$BDey're all over the island. Bring me some cat pelts.
QuestData.RewardText: Dese are some fine pelts, $G boy:girl;. We could make some hefty cloaks outta dese.
